# Grafana Dashboards Directory
#
# This directory will contain pre-configured Grafana dashboards in JSON format.
#
# Recommended dashboards to import:
# 1. Spring Boot 2.1 System Monitor (ID: 11378)
# 2. PostgreSQL Database (ID: 9628)
# 3. Redis Dashboard (ID: 11835)
# 4. Node Exporter Full (ID: 1860)
#
# To import:
# 1. Open Grafana (http://localhost:3000)
# 2. Click + → Import
# 3. Enter dashboard ID
# 4. Select Prometheus datasource
# 5. Click Import
#
# Custom dashboards will also be placed here and auto-loaded on startup.
